          "Nobody can merge while the build is broken",
          "The person who broke it must fix it immediately",
          "&ldquo;Fix it later&rdquo; means it gets worse"
        ]
      },
      {
        "quote": "Professional rule: A broken build is the #1 priority."
      }
    ]
  },
